Package: geneSCOPE
Type: Package
Title: Spatial Gene Co-Occurrence of Pairwise Expression (geneSCOPE)
Version: 1.1.0
Depends: R (>= 4.4.0),
    data.table
Maintainer: Shicheng Zhang <0322704@ed.tus.ac.jp>
Author: Shicheng Zhang [aut, cre] (ORCID: 0000-0003-1608-1039)
Authors@R: 
    c(
